{"id":36,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":36,"title":"Chapter 33: King-Men versus Freemen","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 33","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 33"],["h1","King-Men versus Freemen"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p3"},"Some Nephites wanted the chief judge, Pahoran, to change some of the laws."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.2-3"},"Alma 51:2–3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p5"},"When Pahoran refused, the people became angry and wanted to remove Pahoran as chief judge. They wanted to have a king, not judges."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.3-5"},"Alma 51:3–5"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p7"},"Called king-men, they hoped that one of them would become king and have power over the people."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.5,8"},"Alma 51:5, 8"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p9"},"The Nephites who wanted to keep Pahoran as chief judge were called freemen. They wanted to be free to live and worship as they chose."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.6"},"Alma 51:6"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p11"},"The people voted between the freemen and the king-men. Most of them voted for the freemen."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.7"},"Alma 51:7"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p13"},"At the same time, Amalickiah was gathering a large army of Lamanites to attack the Nephites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.9"},"Alma 51:9"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p15"},"When the king-men heard that the Lamanites were coming, they were pleased and refused to help defend their country."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.13"},"Alma 51:13"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p17"},"Captain Moroni was angry with the king-men for not fighting. He had worked hard to keep the Nephites free."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.14"},"Alma 51:14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p19"},"He asked the governor for the power to make the king-men either fight the Lamanites or be put to death."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.15"},"Alma 51:15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p21"},"When the governor, Pahoran, gave Moroni this power, Moroni led his army against the king-men."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.16-18"},"Alma 51:16–18"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_036_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p23"},"Many king-men were killed; some were put into prison. The rest agreed to help defend their country against the Lamanites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-33-king-men-versus-freemen.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.19-20"},"Alma 51:19–20"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
